<chapter id="rules_and_tips"><title>Game Rules</title> 

<sect1 id="basics">
<title>Game Basics</title>

<para>To make a valid move you have to click to one of the current player's pits. There has to be at least one stone in a pit to move be valid, otherwise you can't do that move. 
</para>
</sect1>

<sect1 id="Rules">
<title>Game Rules</title>

<para>If you make a valid move, then stones are distributed counterclockwise way one by one.</para>
<para>If last stone is placed in your store/treasury you have an extra turn and you play again.</para>
<para>When last stone is placed in your empty pit, now you capture stones from your opponent's opposite pit.</para>
</sect1>

</chapter>

